1 Sec. 7. Original section 81-1230, Reissue Revised Statutes of
2 Nebraska, section 58-703, Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2024,
3 and sections 76-901, 76-903, 77-1327, and 81-1239, Revised Statutes
4 Supplement, 2025, are repealed.
